Saturday 8 Oct }

Mended & read in A.M.  J.C. Smith and H.H. Given came about noon - Left N.York last Monday reached Little Muddy last Eve - Letter fr. Eliab - Given says the down Easter and sucker? look very much alike! I wonder if it be so - Smith brought three pretty pieces of new music - He and Given held Mayo almost all the while - Given wheeled  him to sleep at night - I made white muslin apron in P.M.  Isaac went to Big Muddy but came home before night -

Sabbath 9 Oct -}

 I went to meeting and Isaac stayed with Mayo - Mr Bird preached very well indeed - Mr Rowley came about eleven - not very well -

- I have solemnly promised before God & man to give to God my all - my whole life am I thi?s? doing?  Let me prayerfully examine -
